        <p>Ranitidine is a histamine-2 blocker medication used to reduce the production of stomach acid and treat conditions such as heartburn, acid indigestion, and gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD). It works by blocking the action of histamine, a chemical in the body that stimulates the production of stomach acid.</p>
    </li>
