        <h2>Metformin</h2>
        <p>Metformin is a biguanide medication used to treat type 2 diabetes by controlling blood sugar levels. It works by decreasing the amount of sugar produced by the liver and increasing the sensitivity of muscle cells to insulin, allowing for better glucose uptake and utilization.</p>
